name: Starting with GitHub for EC Students
tagline: This is a tutorial for new users
body:
### Welcome to the Getting Started Page!

This page will link you to a part of GitHub that will help you get started making some really cool stuff.
* *First* make an account on [GitHub.com](https://github.com).
* *Then*, come back here and click the link below. This will take you to the wiki of a sample project that we have set up to help get you started.

[Take me to the wiki!!](https://github.com/Eastside-Catholic/Tutorial/wiki)

(Most of the information you will need from now on can be found in the wiki of this repository that the link takes you to)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
